Lisa Su

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search



Lisa T. Su





Born
1969 (age 47–48)
Tainan, Taiwan


Residence
Texas, United States


Nationality
Chinese


Alma mater
Massachusetts Institute of Technology


Occupation
Business executive, electrical engineer


