2 Career

2.1 1994-1999: Texas Instruments and IBM R&D
2.2 2000-2007: IBM Emerging Products division
2.3 2007-2011: Freescale Semiconductor
2.4 2012-2014: AMD appointments
2.5 2015-2016: AMD diversification


