Lisa T. Su



Dr. Lisa T. Su is Semiconductor Director at Global Semiconductor Alliance, Independent Director at Analog Devices, Inc. and President, CEO & Non-Independent Director at Advanced Micro Devices, Inc. She  is on the Board of Directors at Analog Devices, Inc., Advanced Micro Devices, Inc. and Semiconductor Industry Association. 
Dr. Su was previously employed as Senior VP & GM-Networking & Multimedia Group by Freescale Semiconductor, Inc., VP-Semiconductor Research & Development by International Business Machines Corp., Vice President-Technology Development by Alliancesphere LLC, and Member-Technical Staff by Texas Instruments, Incorporated. 
She received his undergraduate degree from Massachusetts Institute of Technology, a graduate degree from Massachusetts Institute of Technology and a doctorate degree from Massachusetts Institute of Technology. 



